Victor LOPEZ ORTIZ, Appellant/Petitioner(s),
v.
STATE of Florida, Appellee/Respondent(s). CASE NO.: 2D18-4112 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Second District. November 13, 2018

BY ORDER OF THE COURT:

The petition for writ of prohibition is denied without prejudice. Cf. Sumner v. Sumner, 707 So. 2d 934 (Fla. 2d DCA 1998).

KELLY, LUCAS, and ATKINSON, JJ., Concur.
